1. 定义和树图级别关系：
$$\Delta_{GT}=1-\frac{m_N g_A}{f_\pi g_{\pi NN}},\qquad
m_N g_{A,0}=f_\pi g_{\pi NN}\,. $$

2. 展开 $g_A=g_{A,0}+\delta g_A$：
$$\frac{m_N g_A}{f_\pi g_{\pi NN}}
=\frac{g_{A,0}+\delta g_A}{g_{A,0}}
=1+\frac{\delta g_A}{g_{A,0}},$$
因此
$$\Delta_{GT}
=1-\Bigl(1+\frac{\delta g_A}{g_{A,0}}\Bigr)
=-\frac{\delta g_A}{g_{A,0}}\,. $$

3. 单圈手征对数：
$$\delta g_A^{(Z)}
=-\frac{2g_{A,0}^3}{(4\pi f_\pi)^2}m_\pi^2\ln\frac{m_\pi^2}{\mu^2},\quad
\delta g_A^{(V)}
=-\frac{g_{A,0}}{(4\pi f_\pi)^2}m_\pi^2\ln\frac{m_\pi^2}{\mu^2}.$$

4. 对贡献求和：
$$\delta g_A
=\delta g_A^{(Z)}+\delta g_A^{(V)}
=-\frac{g_{A,0}(2g_{A,0}^2+1)}{(4\pi f_\pi)^2}\,
m_\pi^2\ln\frac{m_\pi^2}{\mu^2}\,. $$

5. Goldberger-Treiman 偏差修正：
$$\delta\Delta_{GT}
=-\frac{\delta g_A}{g_{A,0}}
=\frac{2g_{A,0}^2+1}{(4\pi f_\pi)^2}\,
m_\pi^2\ln\frac{m_\pi^2}{\mu^2}\,. $$
